---
title: Classic Chicken Schnitzel & Mayo with Radish, Mint & Parmesan Salad
description: It’s our favourite time of the week again, it’s chicken snitty night! Give it up for this golden crumb with a dollop of
mayo for dipping. This all-star shines brighter with a serving of lush radish and mint salad.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
